      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that makes sense. i think i'll use the unique_ptr approach. one thing tho, i was looking at the logs and it seems like some of these objects aren't being destroyed even when the function finishes, almost like they're being hidden or tucked away somewhere in the system. does using make_unique completely prevent those kinds of hidden issues or could something still be lurking in the background?",
